NECRONOMICON
================================================================================
NECRONOMICON contains resources from `[R...E]` used by various [hdt]
applications, such as texture names.

Components
================================================================================
data
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Resources used to map data to 'things'

necronomicon
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- MoonScript module to parse data
- Provides access to resource mapping in a straight-forward way

Usage
================================================================================
The environment variable 'NECRONOMICON_DATA_PATH' must be defined. It should
point to the 'data' directory.

